### Shopping Mall - Cart API 테스트
### VS Code REST Client Extension 사용

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. 장바구니 조회
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 2. 장바구니 아이템 개수 조회
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. 장바구니에 상품 추가
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "상품_ID_입력",
  "quantity": 1,
  "selectedColor": "흰색",
  "selectedSize": "M"
}

### ============================================
### 4. 장바구니에 상품 추가 (색상/사이즈만 다름)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "상품_ID_입력",
  "quantity": 2,
  "selectedColor": "검은색",
  "selectedSize": "L"
}

### ============================================
### 5. 장바구니 아이템 수량 변경
### ============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/items/아이템_ID_입력
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### ============================================
### 6. 장바구니 아이템 삭제
### ============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/items/아이템_ID_입력
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 7. 장바구니 비우기
### ============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

